melawan atasan mereka.

320
00:16:48,769 --> 00:16:49,769
Hakim Im.

321
00:16:50,210 --> 00:16:52,509
Apa yang ingin kamu katakan?

322
00:16:52,509 --> 00:16:55,509
Katamu kita harus memprotes sesuai aturan.

323
00:16:55,509 --> 00:16:57,979
"Sesuai aturan" bukan berarti "secara antusias",

324
00:16:57,979 --> 00:17:00,119
