325
00:17:00,119 --> 00:17:01,950
Kita harus meyakinkan mayoritas.

326
00:17:03,690 --> 00:17:04,820
Dengan tenang

327
00:17:05,749 --> 00:17:06,889
dan objektif.

328
00:17:08,659 --> 00:17:09,720
Paham?

329
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:13,259
Terkadang omelanmu berguna juga.

